      "instruction": "<p>Once the wedges have been in the oven for 10 mins, add the <strong>chicken burger patties</strong> to a separate tray (use <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong> to prevent them from sticking!) and put the tray in the oven for 12 min or until starting to brown</p>\n<p> </p>",
