        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken burgers have had 12 min, remove the tray from the oven and top them with the <strong>grated cheese</strong> </p>\n<p>Add the <strong>brioche rolls</strong>, cut-side up, to the other side of the tray</p>\n<p>Return the tray to the oven for 3 min or until the cheese has melted and the burgers are cooked through (no pink meat!) – these are your <strong>melty chicken burgers</strong></p>",
