      "instruction": "<p>Assemble the <strong>brioche rolls</strong> with a handful of finely <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>,<strong> </strong>your <strong>melty chicken burger</strong> and <strong>hickory smoked BBQ sauce</strong></p>\n<p>Serve the <strong>potato wedges</strong> and<strong> remaining shredded lettuce </strong>to the side</p>\n<p>Drizzle the <strong>lettuce</strong> with some<strong> olive oil</strong></p>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
